cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper deals with multi-person tracking using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for classification and location prediction also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of online learning and updating of instance-subnets, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The tracking of multiple persons also involves robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
